OL,3,CFamily say crash victim was 'a big kid
OL,4,Cwith a heart of gold'
OL,6,FIn a tribute, his family said it is
OL,7,F"with a heavy heart" that they
OL,8,Fannounced his death.
OL,10,FThey said: "David was a proud father,
OL,11,Fdevoted partner and loyal friend,
OL,12,Floved by many. He enjoyed many years
OL,13,Fdevoted to working at Avon Tyres and
OL,14,Fspent every day of retirement keeping
OL,15,Fbusy and doing what he loved most.
