OL,3,CFamily say crash victim was 'a big kid
OL,4,Cwith a heart of gold'
OL,6,F"David loved the outdoors, and was
OL,7,Foften spotted around Melksham while
OL,8,Frunning, cycling and riding his
OL,9,Fmotorbike with his friends - none of
OL,10,Fwhich would ever be complete without
OL,11,Fan ice-cream.
OL,13,FThey added: "David always made time
OL,14,Ffor others, and he'd be right there
OL,15,Fwhen you needed him. He will be missed
OL,16,Fso very much. We ask those who knew
OL,17,FDavid to respect our wishes for some
OL,18,Fprivacy while we navigate this
OL,19,Funbearable time."
